|-
|'''mouth_name'''
| mouth name, if any (can be Mekong Delta etc.), or the name of the river or sea into which this one flows
|'''mouth_name_note'''
|-
|'''mouth_location *'''
| mouth location
|'''mouth_location_note'''
|-
|'''mouth_lat_d **'''
